{"type": "article", "id": 32188, "title": "Ralph Lauren“即看即买”，以及，秋天来双刺激一点的袜子吧！ | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-09-14T02:20:39Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 2532, "name": "袜子"}, {"id": 4556, "name": "G-Shock"}, {"id": 17109, "name": "atmos"}, {"id": 32762, "name": "溥仪眼镜"}, {"id": 32763, "name": "北欧文具"}, {"id": 681, "name": "Ralph Lauren"}, {"id": 1864, "name": "Tiffany"}, {"id": 2325, "name": "Old Navy"}, {"id": 2326, "name": "Gap"}, {"id": 2897, "name": "玛莎百货"}, {"id": 8195, "name": "Banana Republic"}, {"id": 32759, "name": "Happy Socks"}, {"id": 17322, "name": "Gigi Hadid"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 42, "image": "img/article/article_show/201609140811165igHpcb0FjYLwKX2.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/old-navy-banana-republic-gap-inc-survey-rbc-brian-tunick-10543210/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Old Navy 第二季度表现良好</b></a> | 对于 Gap 集团来说，Old Navy 第二季度表现超预期，Banana Republic 则情况堪忧。第二季度，整个 Gap 集团的业绩下降了 3%，其中 Banana Republic 下降了 9%，Old Navy 业绩持平。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"http://www.theindustrylondon.com/marks-spencer-multi-channel-director-departs/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>玛莎百货的多渠道主管离职</b></a> | 玛莎百货宣布它的多渠道主管  Laura Wade-Gery 正式离职。 Laura Wade-Gery 在 2011 年从乐购加入玛莎百货，主要负责玛莎百货的电商业务的整体运营。</p><p><a href=\"https://www.businessoffashion.com/articles/news-analysis/a-guide-to-fashion-immediacy\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Ralph Lauren 也开始了“即看即买”</b></a> | Ralph Lauren 宣布在 9 月14 日纽约时装周上，也开始了“即看即买”。当场发布的 2016 秋冬季新作的 45 款造型可以立即在店内进行购买。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/stocks-selloff-tiffanys-new-cfo-kate-spade-10542972/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Tiffany &amp; Co 将任命新的 CFO</b></a> | Mark Erceg 将接替 Ralph Nicoletti 成为 Tiffany &amp; Co 集团的财务总监，他将于 10 月 18 日正式入职。该消息促使 Tiffany &amp; Co 的股票上涨了 2%，至每股 69.5 美元。&nbsp;</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p class=\"\">瑞典袜子品牌 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/9/happy-socks-2016\" rel=\"nofollow\">Happy Socks 发布 2016 秋季系列 lookbook</a>。这一季带来了如青柠、折纸、汽球、星星等等丰富的图案设计。造型特辑则延续了品牌的开心搞怪的风格。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609141008243OxyDA5rVaTdEZKw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609141008247ej50Cg4zLGyqsMb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609141008251mGgOV94Y3oBhw8R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160914100825TJuYRoirNeOsD1xa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160914100826eanQwCoTLvDxXAW5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609141008276NP0EmUZSHBv2keA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160914100829izRG97qgh8pB0HKy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160914100830JxvL7WDG2hPASYaB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160914100830jbYCXqMKyG18AN2t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160914100830KCSFONQhnqP3grI9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160914100831WzpysOoehQiKZTF1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/9/oliver-peoples-x-puyi-15-years-anniversary\" rel=\"nofollow\">奢侈眼镜品牌溥仪眼镜庆祝 15 周年，与&nbsp;OLIVER PEOPLES 合作推出了联名系列</a>，带来了独特的大理石蓝玳瑁色款。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160914100807FLCMvQTcg6xBE3le.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160914100807pRSKHQbla3F7hZ8D.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://popbee.com/lifestyle/home-and-living/kikki-k-cute-sweet-collection/\" rel=\"nofollow\">推荐一个来自北欧的文具品牌 kikki.K </a>，它主打简洁的款式以及丰富的颜色，配以可爱的动物图案，显得少女气息满满。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609141007574Ok50Q2PMoBZCrdl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016091410075785UeklXar9m7stbP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160914100757BxzmqIlGPUYQadMV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160914100757vT3zQWdnahODoq8e.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160914100757L3s8crlyVheUv2Pw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160914100758cW793A2dCSHzn16g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">日本知名潮店 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/9/g-shock-x-berbrick-x-atmos-dw-6900\" rel=\"nofollow\">atmos 与 G-SHOCK &nbsp;及 BE@RBRICK 联名推出 DW-6900</a> 表款。同时，atmos 与 BE@RBRICK 推出限量版联名 100% 及 400% 玩偶套装。DW-6900 腕表与 BE@RBRICK 玩偶套装定价分别为 14,800 及 9,200 日元，将于 9 月 24 日正式上架。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><